title: Omnibyte
author: Omnibyte
content: My rate is 8%. Don't expect me to go first. You can reach me on discord at Francisdp#0902 or telegram at Earlyman 22

comments.author: paid2
comments.body: 8% seems a bit much to do business with someone who has no reputation, and who would like me to send the funds first.Plus you don't mention the use of an escrow, it doesn't smell good to be honest.
